.SS AE_MAP (struct action_map)
.PP
This is a container that associates the number of array items with
the array of
.B AE_ITEM
elements.
This allows other functions that use the array to safely access
the elements without overrunning the memory.
.PP
There is a macro,
.BR INIT_MAP ,
that can be used to set the member of the
.B AE_MAP
item.
.PP
.p_AE_MAP
.TP
.BI "AE_ITEM * " items
should be a pointer to an array of
.B AE_ITEM.

